title: January 6 committee still expects Giuliani to 'cooperate fully' despite rescheduled appearance - CNN
content:
1. January 6 committee still expects Giuliani to 'cooperate fully' despite rescheduled appearance  CNN
  2. Rudy Giuliani signaled to the January 6 committee that he'll take a 'less confrontational' stance towards requests for information: NYT report  Yahoo News
  3. Kinzinger says January 6 committee "fully" expects Giuliani to comply with subpoena  Face the Nation

description: Rudy Giuliani has been engaging with the House select committee investigating the January 6 insurrection through his lawyer about the scope of his subpoena and whether he may be able to comply with some requests.
